    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >It is October 14, 2002.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you take on the role of <strong>Chichi Pyonma</strong>. She's a 15-year-old high school student from the unremarkable small town of Silver Bay, MN. Today is a particular day — a rather important one — that drastically shaped Chichi's adolescence from this point onward. It is not for the faint of heart. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238160/extras/dc808f7f93be92b4bd0150fa3bc17ac9.avif?t=1737060015\" width=216 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Before playing this short experience, it is highly recommend that you delve into the contents of pyonpyon87's blog. This is a companion piece to Niomi's debut full-length record, <strong>'chichi'</strong>.</i> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A short interactive story!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From when you boot up the game, to the moment it inevitably closes on you, <strong><i>oct 14</i></strong> serves to tell a short, atmospherically rich, and (mostly) historically accurate story that allows the player to live a few minutes in Chichi's world from a top-down RPG perspective. <i>There is only <strong>one</strong> ending.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238160/extras/9c9fe45046f37b1fc101ca6eaaf7510c.poster.avif?t=1737060015\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238160/extras/9c9fe45046f37b1fc101ca6eaaf7510c.webm?t=1737060015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238160/extras/9c9fe45046f37b1fc101ca6eaaf7510c.mp4?t=1737060015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >​</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In-depth environmental flavor text!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can interact with just about every object in the environment. You'll get a little bit of world-building every time you do! Never skip over the details, you never know what you could be missing...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238160/extras/9e559115b6828c8d0494e803c776b2c0.poster.avif?t=1737060015\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238160/extras/9e559115b6828c8d0494e803c776b2c0.webm?t=1737060015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238160/extras/9e559115b6828c8d0494e803c776b2c0.mp4?t=1737060015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >​</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A period-accurate <i>MPEG Audio Layer 3</i> playback device!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In other words, it's a working MP3 player, and it still has a couple songs on it too! Isn't that cool? However, in order to access it, you might have to snoop around places you shouldn't be.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238160/extras/5d8e9f49392354c77b431c0dae3c2421.poster.avif?t=1737060015\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238160/extras/5d8e9f49392354c77b431c0dae3c2421.webm?t=1737060015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238160/extras/5d8e9f49392354c77b431c0dae3c2421.mp4?t=1737060015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >​</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cute character portraits!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everyone's favorite anxiety-ridden teenager gets her own set of handcrafted facial expressions that appear during dialogue! <i>These talking heads, as well as the game's art and visual assets as a whole, were all drawn by Niomi.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238160/extras/9aacb5afe45e3b8213fea03594f88f94.poster.avif?t=1737060015\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238160/extras/9aacb5afe45e3b8213fea03594f88f94.webm?t=1737060015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238160/extras/9aacb5afe45e3b8213fea03594f88f94.mp4?t=1737060015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >​</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crusty rag!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crusty rag.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238160/extras/84e3be285ba839eeea56f3eb1772c7c3.poster.avif?t=1737060015\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238160/extras/84e3be285ba839eeea56f3eb1772c7c3.webm?t=1737060015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238160/extras/84e3be285ba839eeea56f3eb1772c7c3.mp4?t=1737060015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p>",
